    <tr>
      <td>Once this page has loaded, you will then need to change the mode, it will originally be set to public and youll need to change it to private.&nbsp;</td>
      <td>After the mode has been changed the page will then look like this where other settings will need to be changed. First you will need to change the host to iot.eclipse.org. Secondly change the Port to 1883, and thirdly turn the TLS and Authentication OFF.&nbsp;</td>
      <td>After you have made all of these changes the page should look like this and the data of your location will now be streamed to the website.&nbsp;</td>
      
    </tr>
